<item>
            <title>[NET-614] IMAP fails to quote/encode mailbox names</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/NET-614</link>
                <project id="12310487" key="NET">Commons Net</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Mailbox names need to be quoted if they contain spaces or double-quote.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If they contain non-ASCII characters then they also need to be encoded &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There may be other parameters that are not being encoded/quoted correctly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3501#section-5.1.3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3501#section-5.1.3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
